		<p>
			I have around 10 years of professional experience and lots of silly
			side projects. Nowadays mostly Scala, Java and sometimes .NET(C#). I
			am passionate about my work, always looking for better ways for
			solving current problems both for my private projects and my
			clients.
		</p>
	</div>
</div>

